---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Essential Oil Candle Workshop"
  description="Create luxurious candles using pure essential oils. Premium aromatherapy experience in Centerville, TN."
  price="$28-38 per person"
  duration="2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="essential oil candles, aromatherapy candles, luxury candles, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Essential Oil Candle Workshop - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>
      Experience the luxury and therapeutic benefits of creating candles with pure essential oils. This premium workshop teaches you how to harness the power of aromatherapy through beautifully crafted, scent-blended candles.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      Learn the art of blending pure essential oils with premium soy wax to create luxurious aromatherapy candles. Our experts guide you through proper essential oil selection, blending ratios, and pouring techniques to ensure your candles deliver maximum therapeutic benefits.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Essential oils and aromatherapy education</li>
      <li>Selection of 20+ pure essential oils</li>
      <li>Blending guidance from experts</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax and containers</li>
      <li>Professional pouring instruction</li>
      <li>Take home 2-3 essential oil candles</li>
      <li>Aromatherapy guide for your scents</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Aromatherapy enthusiasts, wellness-focused individuals, and anyone seeking therapeutic candles. Great for creating personalized wellness gifts.
    </p>

    <h3>Essential Oil Profiles</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Relaxation Blends (lavender, chamomile, ylang-ylang)</li>
      <li>Energy Boosters (peppermint, lemon, eucalyptus)</li>
      <li>Immunity Support (tea tree, oregano, frankincense)</li>
      <li>Sleep Support (cedarwood, bergamot, sandalwood)</li>
      <li>Focus & Clarity (rosemary, basil, grapefruit)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Essential oils and aromatherapy introduction (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Explore essential oil options and benefits (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Blend your custom essential oil candle (25 minutes)</li>
      <li>Pour and finish your candles (30 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home and enjoy the therapeutic benefits!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $28-38 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-6 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Create your therapeutic candles!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Love the focus on essential oils! I created candles that actually help me relax. Worth every penny!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Charlotte D.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"As someone into wellness, this was perfect. I have therapeutic candles that smell amazing!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Michael C.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Made aromatherapy candles for the whole family. This is now a favorite wellness gift!"</em></p>
